property.name: note
property.value:
The event focuses on vertical layering by adding a new stem with the local parameter "ProgressionMusic" after the player progress.
"ProgressionMusic"
0: Drone Pad melody 1: + Bell melody 2: + Sitar and clean guitar enters and is layering the pad melody 3: + Marimba layers the bell melody 4: + Drums & Bass 5: - Drums + Guitar Mute, Arp 1, Marimba Lead. 6: - Everything except pad and sitar + Arp 2 (Automation transition straight to value 9 when the box cutscene is triggered. 7: - 8: - 9: + Drums, bass, Clean guitar, Guitar mute, Marimba lead, Lead, Rythm guitar, Guitar lead 10: - Guitar lead, Guitar Mute, Lead, Marimba Lead + Guitar Lead v2, Arp 3, Marimba, Sitar, Layer bell.
(By value 11 the "Sections" parameter changes value to Loop B in unity) 11: 12: - Everything except, Pad, Layer Bell, Arp 1 13: - Arp 1
"Sections" parameter changes to Loop B when the "ProgressionMusic" parameter has the value 11. The transition is playing when the second box cutscene triggers. Loop B has new stems and uses a different time signature.
"Combat" Parameter fades in a sound named "Drone"(Panning modulation) and "Battle Hat" when the player is close to an enemy. The parameter also fades out some conflicting stems if they would play at the same time.
